Hi, my account has a rejected profile message. Could you help me resolve this issue?

I'm sorry to hear about the issue with your profile. It seems that we were unable to verify the business details you provided with information from our verification sources. This means we couldn't confirm that the business information matches a legitimate business entity. If you believe this is an error, or if you have additional documentation that can help us verify your business, please contact our Ad Support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com. They'll be happy to work with you to resolve this issue.
You're welcome! If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out. Thanks for contacting us and we want to hear from you!
